* Iron looked down the hall where Prowl had disappeared down, feeling bad. 
But she had a whole CITY to run now.
She sighed heavily.*

" Perfect!"

* She started to walk down another hall.*

" I'm the mayor of Slag Town."

* Iron Raptor opened a comm to the Maximals.*

" All Maximals! Since most of you are converged infront of the city, I 
expect the rest of you go there and join the crowd too.  I'll be there in a 
few moments to instruct our next course of action.  Iron out."

* From there she began to walk towards the front of the city.*
